il\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"victims\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"food contamination\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The testing agency's stats for the top 25 national delegations show that 98 per cent of Chinese Olympic competitors have been tested multiple times this year.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9512751037853426, \"rank\": 0.0511295568231332, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The testing agency's stats\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"the top 25 national delegations\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"98 per cent\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the Individual Neutral Athletes (AIN) from Russia and Belarus and Hungarians come close, both at 97 per cent.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999994547579, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AIN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.574866217575822, \"rank\": 0.7395309033910452, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9999973319033084, \"rank\": 2.667523724539074e