"ngram\": \"French\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ITA's list showed that the only delegation to undergo 100 per cent testing were AIN entrants - made of Russian and Belarusians - although, at the last count, there are just 33 of them.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9034595830302459, \"rank\": 0.10441831689088907, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999994547579, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AIN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarusians\", \"score\": 0.9999999282511024, \"rank\": 7.17489215537211e-08, \"text\": \"Belarusians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarusians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarusians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only delegation\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"the last count\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, only 63 per cent of footballers have been tested.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 63 per cent\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"footballers\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Global football federation Fifa is one of the few international bodies not to have entrusted their anti-doping programme to the ITA.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2658, \"end\": 2661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9034595830302459, \"rank\": 0.10441831689088907, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Global football federation Fifa\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the few international bodies\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"their anti-doping programme\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ITA took over the Olympic anti-doping programme ahead of the Tokyo Games and now works with most international sports federations.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9034595830302459, \"rank\": 0.10441831689088907, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic anti-doping programme\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"most international sports federations\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ITA said its experience in Tokyo had allowed it to \\\"detect gaps\\\".\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9034595830302459, \"rank\": 0.10441831689088907, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Television_Autho